story.title: Littlefield - Part 1
story.storyDescription: Sarah finds a dead body in the woods and uncovers a dark and deadly mystery.

messages.text: Wayne, please be there…
pls pls pls
ANSWER ME!!!!
What’s going on?
Just got home.
I’m in the North Woods.
What the hell are you doing in the North Woods!?
I found a dead body.
WHAT!? Like a human body??!!
yeah. and now i’m being followed
it was disgusting Wayne
his guts were hanging out
I leaned over to see who it was
and then someone lunged at me from behind!!
Where are you exactly?
I’m hiding in a cove near some bog. I’m scared.
Please help me.
Did you call the cops?
No, I can’t call the cops. Then my parents will know I snuck out
ARE YOU OUT OF YOUR FUCKING MIND!? YOU HAVE TO CALL THE COPS!
What if the person who was running behind me hears me??
I’ll call them.
NO, DON’T…
Then what!? I don’t know what else to do here!?
Do you think maybe you could come get me??
How am I supposed to come get you!?
My phone map says I’m near the southern tip.
I can send you a drop pin and I could meet you at the closest exit
Does the drop pin show where the murderer is located on the map!?!
I’m calling the cops Sarah
DON’T. You don’t know my Dad!
He can’t be any worse than a fucking MURDERER
Please, Wayne.
I don’t understand what you want the plan to be then.
Or what plan won’t end up in both of us being DEAD here.
Didn’t you say your Dad has a gun?
Yeah, he has several, but I don’t know how to USE THEM
All you have to do is scare them off if they come close
What if they have a gun??
They would’ve shot me with it already
Wayne please.
I don’t understand why out of all people you’re calling me!?
You’ve only known me for two weeks!
You seem like someone I can trust
My Dad is right downstairs. There’s no way to get the gun out
Just please figure something out
I think if I remember correctly he has one in the spare bedroom.
Please look!
I’M LOOKING.
I still don’t understand what I’m going to do with it...
since I don’t know how to aim and shoot anything
Maybe you can cause a distraction?
And I can run out in the opposite direction, and we can meet at Burger Alley
That’s the dumbest idea of all time.
What the fuck are you even DOING out there??
I wanted to take a shortcut home from the party.
Unbelievable.
Oh my God, I can hear him coming
Okay, just stay still.
Is he saying anything??
Grunting noises. It sounds like there’s more than one person
I called the cops. I’m sorry I had to do it.
NO! FUCK YOU WAYNE!
Don’t worry, I’m driving there too.
We can figure something out so you don’t get in trouble
They said that they are on their way. Can you describe where you are??
Sarah??
SARAH???
They're eating a deer
What?!
I poked my head up to see what was going on
ARE YOU INSANE?
And these guys were on the ground just…
eating this deer, tearing into it with their mouths.
Are they distracted enough so that you could make your way any further south?
Towards the main road??
I’m too scared to move
Okay just breathe
Please tell me you’re on your way
I am. I grabbed my Dad’s gun too
Just describe where you are in the woods, so I can tell the cops.
Is it the same place you said before?
Oh my God someone just came and fired a bunch of shots.
I screamed! I think they heard me
RUN!
I can’t
JUST RUN!!
There’s more
More what?? People with guns??
What??
Sarah?
SARAH???
Click below to see what happens next...
